{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call it the Glass House because it had a glass, glass wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where hundreds of Jews have been gathering under the protection of Swiss [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my uncle, the little fellow you have seen on the-- the smallest, youngest boy, who, who was the-- who was a Zionist, he was an ardent Zionist way back in our family, who was the leader of these few hundred people hiding there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I knew that they are very hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my uncle, the baker, give me few basket full of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I take them in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, look, it's very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are surrounded by, by the Arrow Cross people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got a basketful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I put on my leather coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was my most precious worldly possession because leather was, was typical to power, right, military power, right?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a, a, a boot, a, a [HUNGARIAN], we called it, a leather boot, right?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had my other paraphernalia, my, my hat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my-- I put my Arrow Cross band on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went into this what's the name of this house, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I got in, I told them who I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took the band off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spoke to my cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I left the bread there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody asked anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- if you want to be safest, you go to the lion's den.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the safest, right?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anywhere else is considerably more dangerous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My uncle, my other uncle, has been taken away from another, another, another protected house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- his daughter is here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's my double cousin, because two brothers married two sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very interesting situation.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
